<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT21">
<l>ivaiyā pilavāy tiṟanteri kāṉṟa</l>
<l>vivaiyā verivaṭṭak kaṇka ḷivaiyā</l>
<l>veripoṅkik kāṭṭu mimaiyōr perumā</l>
<l>ṉaripoṅkik kāṭṭu maḻaku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is this the cave mouth that opened and spat fire out?</l>
<l>Are these the fiery-circle[-like] eyes?</l>
<l>Is this the beauty that the Lord of the unblinking [gods]—</l>
<l>who appeared flaring up [like] fire—presented flaring up [as] a lion?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
